{
  "stem": "3380.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she stopped with the treatment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- I could not convince her to go through with the treatment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the doctor said that she can never bear any children, because she had seven, eight treatments already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, you go every minute-- every time you go for more minutes, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she had almost all-- she was almost through with the treatment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she said no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we went into a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took my wife to a doctor in-- in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was an old-time doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked her if she received quinine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the doctor-- she said, yes, I did receive quinine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I got sick from it and I had to throw it out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what he did is try to put the quinine into-- through a tube, through the stomach, into the intestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for one or another reason, the temperature disappeared, and she start feeling better.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at that point, you felt comfortable to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, she was still in the old people home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was old people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was Passover in 1949.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we decided that we're going to go home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I was living far away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was living not far from Bayreuth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we decided-- I mean, we know that we're going to be together for Passover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because well, I was-- during the five years, we were never together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we know that she can never bear any Children so I didn't try to protect anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she came back to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She find out that she is pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, all the fistulas all closed on her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, she had open wounds in here and in the-- the back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And out of nowhere, the whole thing closed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
